T1  - Working In Retirement: The Antecedents Of Bridge Employment And Its Consequences For Quality Of Life In Retirement
AU  - Kim, Seongsu
AU  - Feldman, Daniel C.
Y1  - 2000/12/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/1556345
