T1  - Frederick W. Taylor'S 1899 Pig Iron Observations: Examining Fact, Fiction, And Lessons For The New Millennium
AU  - Wrege, Charles D.
AU  - Hodgetts, Richard M.
Y1  - 2000/12/01
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/1556350
